name: Max Caulfield | Life is Strange LoRA
description:
Third LoRA of my life is strange collection, soon comes Steph and Alex
This LoRA has more reference images, and finally i found the best training point.

Recommended: use vae vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

Sometimes it makes weird hands and weird face with certains prompts, meaning that a bigger dataset is needed, maybe i will update it tomorrow


LoRA trained with my landscapes model 3.0: https://civitai.com/models/5041/cheese-daddys-landscapes-mix
